"" map CTRL_HJKL to move cursor in all modes
" some old terminal softwares will send ^H for <backspace> by default,
" " change your terminal settings to bind <backspace> to ASCII code 127.
" "----------------------------------------------------------------------
noremap <C-h> <left>
noremap <C-j> <down>
noremap <C-k> <up>
noremap <C-l> <right>
inoremap <C-h> <left>
inoremap <C-j> <down>
inoremap <C-k> <up>
inoremap <C-l> <right>

